name: MJfurry
description:
200 midjourny realistic style furry images trained on ayonimix, 150 of which are military-armed furry, so it should be good at that.

It works on many models, such as the anything series and ayonimix. It can also create things that go beyond the training set but better than base model, such as human characters with gorgeous backgrounds in only 3 words. I don't know why.

Realistic images with tags: realistic, photorealistic, 8k, RAW photo, etc.

Or anime style if you want.

If you find any potential in this model, let me know in the comment.

Set the weight to about 0.75

If you are not satisfied with the low resolution image, please use Hires. fix
